" ==========================================================
" GVim/MacVim Configuration (Self-contained)
" ==========================================================
" This is a standalone configuration for MacVim/GVim.
" It does NOT source _vimrc to avoid nvim-specific code.

" ==========================================================
" Plugins (Vim-compatible only, no nvim plugins)
" ==========================================================

